<em>Published in final edited form as: </em>IEEE/ACM Trans Comput Biol Bioinform. 2016 Jul 14;14(3):555–563. doi: <a href="https://doi.org/10.1109/TCBB.2016.2591539" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">10.1109/TCBB.2016.2591539</a>
